{"tid":311207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續打香港人荷包, 以後每部電器收最高 165蚊再造費","createTime":"2017-07-06T12:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T21:01:01.000Z","uid":27240,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f941afe03802168715741893e2728d0d09002e0d","tid":311207,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:10:48.000Z","msg":"電器產品往往是電子污染的源頭 , 不過大多會通過回收分拆部份有價值物料循環再用 . 其實很少會直接整部丟棄 . 不過香港政府喜歡「環保」, 所以昨日香港立法會通過《產品環保責任（受管制電器）規例》, 規定八類電器需要徵收每件15元至165元的循環再造費 , 而新法例將由今年底至明年分階段實施 . 繼續打香港人荷包 .<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/200843_4adda93b58e1c7aa666794e3f0951a7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F200843_4adda93b58e1c7aa666794e3f0951a7b.jpg&h=ed6f00ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環境局局長黃錦星在立法會上表示:「香港每年產生約7萬公噸廢電器電子產品 , 新法例是為推行廢電器電子產品生產者責任計劃訂出的運作細節 .」<br />\n<br />\n根據《產品環保責任（受管制電器）規例》, 規定冷氣機、雪櫃、洗衣機、電視機、電腦、打印機、掃瞄器與顯示器等八類電器設備供應商需要向當局登記受管制電器貨量資料 , 徵收每件15元至165元的循環再造費 . 銷售商須向消費者安排免費移走同類舊產品的服務 , 再把收回的產品送往持牌循環再造商處理 . 相信最終所產生一切費用將由消費者承擔 .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《主體條例》規定，署長在釐定登記供應商須繳付的循環再造徵費後 , 須向供應商送達繳費通知書。循環再造徵費必須在通知書送達後30日內繳交 . 按照「污染者自付」原則 , 受管制電器的循環再造徵費應訂於收回全部成本的水平 . 建議的收費水平與今年一月向環境事務委員會匯報的相同，即：<br />\n<br />\n（一）電視機及<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>電冰箱</strong></span>的收費為每件165元；<br />\n（二）洗衣機及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">空調機</span></strong>的收費為每件125元；<br />\n（三）顯示器的收費為每件45元；以及<br />\n（四）電腦、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">列印機</span></strong>及掃描器的收費為每件15元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你個政府帶頭用埋d 共產中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源: <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/07/06/hk-gov-levied-recycling-costs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2Fhk-gov-levied-recycling-costs%2F&d=1Yex6I4Ej0n%2FmToe9nq7BEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0c1dff79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/07/06/hk-gov-levied-recycling-costs/</a><br />\n<br />\n跟蹤 <a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=1Yex6I4Ej0n%2FmToe9nq7BEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=5c8dee6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a> Facebook 專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/qoooah\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fqoooah&d=1Yex6I4Ej0n%2FmToe9nq7BEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=e82be2c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/qoooah</a>"},{"pid":"dd1bc86f81dfee27056489e3af657a3dc106d822","tid":311207,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"電冰箱即係咩<br />\n電啲冰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776507981c2f75f12a67174175c673be4de3e452","tid":311207,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"香港玩完架啦<br />\n呢班狗官狂掠水<br />\n掠完就去外國嘆世界"},{"pid":"2ab9f27a191f2a2e80abc5feeb211c39b0d4fbfa","tid":311207,"uid":111270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港玩完架啦<br />\n呢班狗官狂掠水<br />\n掠完就去外國嘆世界</blockquote><br />\n是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多聽日早d起身返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528cb1f2e98e41115e805e912c9d706439577777","tid":311207,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:30:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57200cef3c71ac16447bbd968d0b5ef2045341be","tid":311207,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電冰箱即係咩<br />\n電啲冰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港柒、五毛：」電冰箱同雪櫃唔同，電冰箱係可以雪埋冰、雪櫃係雪啲雪出嚟<img s